# General Code Style & Formatting
- Follow the Airbnb Style Guide for code formatting.
- Use PascalCase for Vue component file names (e.g., UserCard.vue, not user-card.vue).
- Prefer named exports for components.

# Project Structure & Architecture
- Follow Vue.js patterns and use the App Router.
- Correctly determine when to use server vs. client components in nuxt.

# Styling & UI
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling.
- Use Shadcn UI for components.

# Data Fetching & Forms
- Use Axios for frontend data fetching.
- Use VeeValidate for form handling.
- Use Zod for validation.

# State Management & Logic
- Use Pinia for state management.

# Backend & Database
- Use Supabase for database access.

# Authentication
- Use Supabase for authentication.

# API
- Use Vite for API development.

# Testing
- Use Jest for testing.

# Deployment
- Use Vercel for deployment.
